params.lockupDays: Initial lockup period before any redemption
params.periodDays: Gate period in days (e.g., 90 for quarterly)

cancelRedemption(uint256).details: Only the original investor can cancel; only pending/queued requests

params.requestId: ID of the request to cancel

createSidePocket(uint256,string).details: Side-pocketed assets are excluded from redemption NAV

params.reason: Description of why asset is being side pocketed

returns.sidePocketId: ID of the created side pocket

distributeSidePocket(uint256).details: Distributes pro-rata to investors who held shares when side pocket was created

returns.lockupEnds: Timestamp when lockup ends (0 if not in lockup)

packedSelectors().details: Each selector is 4 bytes, packed sequentially with no padding      MUST NOT include packedSelectors() itself in the returned selectors      MUST be a pure function (no state access)

returns.wouldBeGated: Whether request would be partially gated

processRedemptions(uint256).details: Processes in FIFO order, respecting gate limits

params.maxRequests: Maximum number of requests to process (0 = all eligible)

recordInvestorEntry(address).details: Called by other facets when investor receives tokens

requestRedemption(uint256).details: Request enters queue; eligible for processing after notice period

returns.requestId: Unique ID for this redemption request

createSidePocket(uint256,string).notice: Create a side pocket for an illiquid investment

distributeSidePocket(uint256).notice: Distribute a side pocket when asset is realized

forceCancelRedemption(uint256,string).notice: Force cancel a redemption request (admin only)

getInvestorRequests(address).notice: Get all pending requests for an investor

getPendingRedemptionCount().notice: Get count of pending/queued redemption requests

isInLockup(address).notice: Check if an investor is in lockup period

isRedemptionControlInitialized().notice: Check if redemption control is initialized

isRedemptionsSuspended().notice: Check if redemptions are currently suspended

packedSelectors().notice: Returns all function selectors for this facet as tightly packed bytes

previewRedemption(uint256).notice: Preview redemption - estimate proceeds for a given share amount

recordInvestorEntry(address).notice: Record when an investor first invests (for lockup tracking)
